description = "A flour-dusted man with powerful arms from years of hauling grain sacks and a perpetually worried expression. Oswin inherited the watermill from his father and has kept it running through every season, but lately something has gone wrong with the mechanism. He spends his days fretting over gears and millstones, convinced the mill is cursed. His knowledge of the lake and its moods is unmatched."
